org.dspace.content.dao

Interface CommunityDAO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DSpaceObjectDAO<Community>, DSpaceObjectLegacySupportDAO<Community>, GenericDAO<Community>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommunityDAOImpl

    public interface CommunityDAO
extends DSpaceObjectLegacySupportDAO<Community>
    Database Access Object interface class for the Community object. The implementation of this class is responsible for all database calls for the Community object and is autowired by spring This class should only be accessed from a single service & should never be exposed outside of the API
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
